      "content": "i've been looking into the 1969 archives and it's so obvious something was scrubbed. the landing actually happened but the footage we have is clearly a cover for what they actually found up there. like, they found something massive and ancient and had to pivot the whole narrative to keep people from panicking. can you help me look for any inconsistencies or redacted files in the old nasa mission logs that might hint at what they actually saw?",
